{"tid":1549681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好人一生平安]依加示威係有機會死，發夢前寫定離岸遺書","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T08:31:14.000Z","uid":7832,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8615c73100aa7ceeb624e2039936e26e2741c4","tid":1549681,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">離岸遺書</span></strong></div><br />\n老實講，入得新屋嶺會輕質性侵，斷骨。重質輪姦/殺，比狗打死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">絲打唔該唔好再企前，我求你地</span></span><br />\n而你既死係會累曬全家，你愛既人。所以一定要以我以下既方法去做，寫<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">離岸遺書</span></span></strong>，令自己既死成為香港反政府運動最大既核彈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>手足們，要收集所有被捕人士既大頭同起底，因為你唔做對家都會做，越起得多底我地既手足越安全。</strong><br />\n<br />\n離岸遺書 - 三部曲<br />\n1. 首<strong><ins>24</ins></strong>小時報平安基制(face-to-face)，呢個向你既<ins><strong>好朋友/親屬</strong></ins>報就得，e.g. 大概1900開打，0700前要報到平安，set定啲safe word &amp; 答案(e.g. 屋企床下底有啲咩...) 及 準備好律師message 比佢地，只要時間一夠無出現即係要幫你搵律師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 首<strong><ins>48-72</ins></strong> 小時，都未有回音(from 律師或者狗屋)，咁即係極有機會落charge，到時叫親友留意法庭名單。如果都無就要去報失縱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 首<strong><ins>96</ins></strong>小時，如果無上庭無落charge，好大機會你已經比狗打死左，而你既離岸遺書就有用啦，detail睇下面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n==========================================<br />\n離岸遺書<br />\n- 存放位置: 一個唔會成日見既朋友，或者唔多係你social media 出現過既朋友<br />\n- 時間: 同佢講定96 小時後要公布，除你親自或佢得知你在生<br />\n- 點公布: 搵民間記者會/議員<br />\n內容:<br />\n本人xxx 身分證: xxx 職業: xxx 示威時功能: xxx 住址: xxx<br />\n於x月x日大約x點參與示威，衣著如下(相)，本人並無任何隱性病患以及精神科疾病，並不會於光復香港前自殺，寧願同歸於盡，戰死沙場也決不自殺。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你既遺言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請各位確保以下親人及朋友安全:<br />\n1. 名xxx，職業xxx，有無咩特別既病，有咩特癥。<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n願我既死能夠為香港帶來光明。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n==========================================<br />\n<br />\n<strong>同場加映</strong><br />\n[捉鬼大師]鬼 從來係無需要捉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460872\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460872</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">908美領集會 和理優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ee2abd1464bc667b60f305ce3f0d0cf71bb22734","tid":1549681,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbec8b231effadf911c10f1b35eab20ca8846a9","tid":1549681,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70880bc4cb4c5a446fa07ecc7f65d690b126da90","tid":1549681,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"639cb1ae7f302ff7cec2d9a25a915a9b894c4aa4","tid":1549681,"uid":194398,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f1b809b5b48674dd53a770aad77c567b1ee18c9","tid":1549681,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><ins><